name: thebluealliance
description: Node.js wrapper for The Blue Alliance v2 API
readme:
# node-thebluealliance   
   node-thebluealliance is a node.js wrapper library for [The Blue Alliance v2 API](http://www.thebluealliance.com/apidocs). See the v2 API page for more information on what data can be returned. This app uses The Blue Alliance's post-2013 [event codes](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0ApRO2Yzh2z01dExFZEdieV9WdTJsZ25HSWI3VUxsWGc#gid=0). 
See the github repo for more details on the project.
